{
  slug: "mip-splatting",
  kind: "milestone",
  title: {
    zh: "Mip-Splatting：无混叠三维高斯泼溅",
    en: "Mip-Splatting: Alias-free 3D Gaussian Splatting",
  },
  summary: {
    zh: "用三维频率约束与二维 Mip 滤波缓解采样率变化时的锯齿与膨胀，实现跨尺度稳定渲染。",
    en: "Uses 3D frequency constraints and a 2D Mip filter to reduce aliasing and dilation when the sampling rate changes.",
  },
  description: {
    zh: "该工作指出原始 3D 高斯泼溅在改变焦距或相机距离时易出现高频伪影，原因包括缺少三维频率约束与二维膨胀滤波。作者依据输入视图的采样极限约束高斯原语尺度，并以近似二维盒式滤波的 Mip 滤波替代膨胀，从而在单尺度训练、多尺度测试等设定下改善画质。实现上对原始 3DGS 改动较小，可与现有管线结合。",
    en: "The paper attributes zoom-related artifacts in 3D Gaussian Splatting to missing 3D frequency limits and the use of a 2D dilation filter. It introduces a 3D smoothing filter tied to the Nyquist limit implied by training views and replaces dilation with a 2D Mip filter that mimics a box filter, reducing aliasing and dilation when focal length or distance changes. The method keeps the explicit Gaussian representation while targeting out-of-distribution sampling rates, with modest code changes over vanilla 3DGS.",
  },
