      zh: "采样定理视角下的三维频率上限，是抑制缩放时伪影的可解释抓手。",
      en: "A sampling-theoretic bound on 3D frequency content gives a principled lever against scale-change artifacts.",
    },
    {
      zh: "屏幕空间滤波器设计需同时考虑物理成像与光栅化近似，Mip 思路可迁移到显式高斯。",
      en: "Screen-space filtering must align both with the imaging model and the rasterizer; Mip-style prefiltering transfers to explicit Gaussians.",
